title: Bali Adventure
description: Explore the beautiful beaches and temples of Bali with guided tours
itinerary: Day 1: Arrival in Ubud - Check into resort - Welcome dinner with traditional Balinese dance | Day 2: Sacred Monkey Forest - Tegallalang Rice Terraces - Ubud Art Market - Cooking class | Day 3: Mount Batur sunrise trek - Hot springs relaxation - Coffee plantation tour | Day 4: Tanah Lot Temple - Jimbaran Beach sunset dinner - Traditional spa treatment | Day 5: Water temple ceremony - Departure

title: Tokyo City Tour
description: Discover modern culture and ancient traditions in Japan's bustling capital
itinerary: Day 1: Arrival in Tokyo - Shibuya Crossing - Harajuku district exploration - Robot restaurant show | Day 2: Senso-ji Temple - Tokyo Skytree - Sumida River cruise - Sushi making class | Day 3: Tsukiji Fish Market - Imperial Palace gardens - Ginza shopping district - Kabuki theater | Day 4: Day trip to Mount Fuji - Lake Kawaguchi - Traditional ryokan experience | Day 5: Meiji Shrine - Takeshita Street - Departure from Narita Airport

title: London Heritage Walk
description: Walk through centuries of history in one of the world's greatest cities
itinerary: Day 1: Arrival - Tower of London - Tower Bridge - Thames River cruise - Welcome dinner at historic pub | Day 2: Westminster Abbey - Big Ben - Houses of Parliament - Churchill War Rooms - Afternoon tea | Day 3: British Museum - Covent Garden - West End theater show - Traditional fish and chips | Day 4: Windsor Castle day trip - Royal gardens - Shopping at Oxford Street - Farewell dinner | Day 5: Buckingham Palace - Hyde Park - Departure

title: New York City Explorer
description: Experience the city that never sleeps from Times Square to Central Park
itinerary: Day 1: Arrival - Times Square exploration - Broadway show - Late night food tour | Day 2: Statue of Liberty - Ellis Island - 9/11 Memorial - Wall Street walking tour | Day 3: Central Park - Metropolitan Museum - 5th Avenue shopping - Empire State Building sunset | Day 4: Brooklyn Bridge walk - DUMBO neighborhood - High Line park - Chelsea Market food hall | Day 5: One World Trade Center - Helicopter tour - Departure from JFK Airport
